              <li><strong>You</strong> (referred to as "Client" or "User") means the individual accessing the Service, or the company or legal entity on whose behalf such individual is acting.</li>
              <li><strong>Statement of Work (SOW)</strong> means a separate signed document defining specific project deliverables, timelines, and payment terms.</li>
              <li><strong>Country</strong> means the United Arab Emirates.</li>
              <li><strong>Device</strong> means any device — computer, mobile phone, or tablet — that can access the Website.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>2. Acknowledgment</h2>
            <p>These Terms and Conditions govern the use of our Service and form a legally binding agreement between you and Aegis AI. By accessing or using the Website, booking a consultation, or engaging our services, you confirm that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms in their entirety.</p>
            <p>You represent that you are at least <strong>18 years of age</strong>. If you are using the Service on behalf of a company or organisation, you represent that you have the authority to bind that entity to these Terms.</p>
            <p>If you do not agree with any part of these Terms, you must discontinue use of the Website and our Services immediately. Access to the Service is also conditioned on your acceptance of our <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>, which describes how we collect, protect, and use your personal data.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>3. Services Offered</h2>
            <p>Aegis AI provides technology consultancy services tailored to Small and Medium Enterprises (SMEs) in Dubai and the wider UAE, specialising in:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Custom AI Development:</strong> Designing and deploying bespoke AI agents, WhatsApp chat automation, databases, and operational dashboards integrated with client workflows.</li>
              <li><strong>AI Training &amp; Workshops:</strong> Delivering departmental upskilling workshops in English and Arabic to ensure internal team adoption.</li>
              <li><strong>AI Strategy &amp; Consulting:</strong> Creating 12-month roadmaps, ROI calculations, and vendor-neutral technology audits.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All specific deliverables, timelines, and payment terms will be defined in a separate signed Statement of Work (SOW) or Service Agreement, which shall take precedence over these generic terms in the event of any conflict.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>4. The 100% Refund Guarantee Policy</h2>
            <div class="guarantee-box">
              <p class="title">Zero-Cost Risk-Free Guarantee</p>
              <p>We are proud to offer a complete refund policy for custom AI development and workshops. Our guarantee is subject to the following standard parameters to protect both parties:</p>
              <ul>
                <li><strong>Defined Success Criteria:</strong> Every project features clear, objectively measurable milestones defined in writing inside the Statement of Work (SOW) before work commences.</li>
                <li><strong>Active Engagement:</strong> The client must provide the necessary credentials, document samples, and attend scheduled alignment sessions required to build the system.</li>
                <li><strong>Guarantee Trigger:</strong> If, at the final delivery stage of the initial defined scope, the custom system or training fails to meet the pre-agreed success criteria despite active collaboration, the client is entitled to request a 100% refund of all development fees paid to date.</li>
