              </ul>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>5. Third-Party API Fees &amp; Retainers</h2>
            <p>Unless explicitly written in the SOW, project fees do not include direct third-party usage fees (e.g., API charges from OpenAI, Anthropic, Microsoft Azure, Make.com, or Meta WhatsApp Business API). These are set up directly on the client's billing accounts or billed transparently at cost with zero mark-up.</p>
            <p>Our development projects include <strong>90 days of complimentary post-launch support</strong> (bug fixes, performance monitoring). Ongoing updates, operational retainer packages, and additional training modules are subject to separate monthly agreements.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>6. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
            <p>Unless otherwise agreed in a signed SOW, upon full and final payment of all invoices, the client is granted a perpetual, worldwide, non-exclusive, non-transferable licence to use the custom software, workflows, and configurations developed specifically for their organisation.</p>
            <p>Aegis AI retains all rights to our pre-built software modules, underlying frameworks, training methodologies, and proprietary AI agents developed prior to or outside of the specific SOW. All content on the Website — including text, graphics, logos, and design — is the exclusive intellectual property of Aegis AI and may not be reproduced without prior written consent.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2>7. Client Responsibilities</h2>
            <p>To ensure timely project delivery (typically 8–12 weeks), you agree to provide:</p>
